name: Scientific Entrepreneur Evaluations
tag_list: investor-consulting, investor-reports, due-diligence, entrepreneur-personality, entrepreneur-assessment, startup-roi
overview:
Scientifically evaluate the Fitness level of entrepreneurs to identify who will succeed.

SEE™ provides clients with scientifically reliable assessments that report on both the candidate’s strengths across key entrepreneurial personality traits and his/her ability to adapt to a changing environment. These assessments are based on the proprietary Prime Reasoning™ ability test and the 16PF® questionnaire, which is widely used by clinical and industrial psychologists to assess key personality traits of individuals. The 16PF® is regarded as one of the most reliable scientific tools in the industry. These assessments are designed to: Help in the entrepreneur funding selection process Provide development insights so that the mentoring and guiding of the entrepreneur is optimized.
